  <body region="amara-subtitle-area">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:13.667" end="00:00:34.233">[clicking]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:35.133" end="00:00:36.541">&#65279;[plane landing]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:37.333" end="00:00:39.833">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] I was flying to New York <br/>to visit this good friend of mine,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:00:40.067" end="00:00:42.641">and just as the plane was landing<br/>I was getting that kind of, you know</p>
      <p begin="00:00:42.641" end="00:00:45.926">fidgety feeling of wanting to check <br/>my cellphone and I was thinking,</p>
      <p begin="00:00:45.926" end="00:00:48.035">it wasn't that long ago<br/>that when a plane landed</p>
      <p begin="00:00:48.035" end="00:00:49.861">we would have lunged<br/>for our cigarette packs.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:50.034" end="00:00:52.600">Well, actually we used to all <br/>smoke on the planes.</p>
      <p begin="00:00:52.967" end="00:00:54.672">[Laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.672" end="00:00:56.808">But nowadays when a plane lands, <br/>we all lunge for our cellphones</p>
      <p begin="00:00:56.808" end="00:00:59.204">that same kind of addictive fever</p>
      <p begin="00:00:59.204" end="00:01:02.296">like we can't stand not being connected <br/>for a second longer.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:02.296" end="00:01:03.519">And it doesn't let up.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:03.519" end="00:01:06.447">Walking down the street in Manhattan<br/>no one is making eye contact.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:06.447" end="00:01:09.159">Everybody is looking down,<br/>they're texting, they're tweeting.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:09.159" end="00:01:10.998">I half expected to see <br/>the Statue of Liberty,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:10.998" end="00:01:14.283">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">torch with one hand, <br/>texting with the other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:01:14.283" end="00:01:16.734">So I'm finally at lunch with this <br/>really good friend of mine,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:16.734" end="00:01:18.909">and we're having a fantastic time --<br/>I haven't seen her in years --</p>
      <p begin="00:01:18.909" end="00:01:20.874">laughing, drinking, talking,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:20.874" end="00:01:23.996">but I'm still getting this urge <br/>to check my email.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:23.996" end="00:01:26.442">I was like, Tiffany stay focused, <br/>you traveled all the way</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26.442" end="00:01:28.821">across the United States <br/>to see her, stay focused.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28.821" end="00:01:31.578">But eventually it was like <br/>it overtook me.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:31.578" end="00:01:34.183">And then I faked needing<br/>to go to the bathroom.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34.183" end="00:01:39.413">So I excused myself, grabbed my phone,<br/>go into the bathroom stall,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:39.413" end="00:01:44.152">kind of hiding, texting, emailing, <br/>thinking, "What have I become?"</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.152" end="00:02:29.698">&#9834; [lively music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:02:29.698" end="00:02:33.874">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Technology is clearly changing us<br/>and the way we connect with our friends</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.874" end="00:02:38.403">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">our families and the world around us.<br/>So I set out to make a film about,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.403" end="00:02:42.387">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">what it means to be connected <br/>in the 21st century.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:42.387" end="00:02:45.435">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For 200,000 years we've been <br/>connecting through networks</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.435" end="00:02:49.257">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">both natural and technological.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:49.257" end="00:02:51.283">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today our networks <br/>have expanded to a point</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:51.283" end="00:02:55.777">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">where the've given the world <br/>a central nervous system.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.777" end="00:02:59.180">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Something happens in one place<br/>and we can see it, feel it</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:59.180" end="00:03:02.732">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and do something about it,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.732" end="00:03:05.917">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which has such huge potential.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:05.917" end="00:03:07.128">[splash]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:07.128" end="00:03:10.991">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But technology has also led<br/>to the biggest problems of our day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:10.991" end="00:03:13.191">[sewing machines rattling]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.191" end="00:03:16.615">[machine gun firing]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:16.615" end="00:03:20.184">[crashing]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:20.184" end="00:03:26.040">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's accelerating our connectedness<br/>in ways we can't even predict.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:26.040" end="00:03:29.161">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Take the honeybees,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:29.161" end="00:03:31.161">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">their recent disappearance<br/>is the perfect example</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.161" end="00:03:34.844">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">of how everything is connected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:34.844" end="00:03:38.345">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Albert Einstein predicted that if<br/>honeybees were to disappear completely,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:38.345" end="00:03:42.638">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">humanity would be gone in four years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:42.638" end="00:03:47.098">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">No more honeybees, <br/>no more food being pollinated,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:47.098" end="00:03:51.292">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">no more humans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:51.292" end="00:03:53.789">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So if one change in our <br/>over-connected world</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:53.789" end="00:03:56.676">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">can have such far-reaching <br/>consequences,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:56.676" end="00:03:59.038">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">how do we use the power <br/>of all these connections</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:03:59.038" end="00:04:03.518">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to turn things around?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:03.518" end="00:04:07.436">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This was the kind of question <br/>I was exploring in this film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:07.436" end="00:04:10.345">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then I had this year<br/>that turned my world upside down.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:10.345" end="00:04:13.931">[siren wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:13.931" end="00:04:16.415">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And forced me to rethink everything <br/>I thought I understood</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.415" end="00:04:17.821">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about the ways we're connected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:17.821" end="00:04:21.815">[siren wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:04:21.815" end="00:04:26.353">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Let me back up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:26.353" end="00:04:30.531">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When I was growing up,<br/>I had my own version of Einstein.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:30.531" end="00:04:33.764">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I called him Dad.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.764" end="00:04:39.059">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was the one who taught me to look <br/>for connections in the first place.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:39.059" end="00:04:42.727">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He was a general surgeon<br/>with a special interest in the brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.727" end="00:04:49.879">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he always found entertaining ways<br/>to teach us about his work.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:49.879" end="00:04:52.488">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When I was in third grade, <br/>he came to my class on career day</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:52.488" end="00:04:54.510">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with a huge ice cream container.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:54.510" end="00:04:55.810">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He put in on the teacher's desk</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:55.810" end="00:04:58.995">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and he started talking <br/>about the human brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:58.995" end="00:05:01.729">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said the way the brain works<br/>is very complicated.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:01.729" end="00:05:05.942">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But a simple way to think about it<br/>is that it has two hemispheres.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:05.942" end="00:05:08.199">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The left brain breaks things down<br/>and creates order,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.199" end="00:05:11.926">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the right brain recognizes patterns <br/>and processes emotions.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:11.926" end="00:05:13.667">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he talked about how <br/>the two hemispheres</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.667" end="00:05:16.445">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">have to work together.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:16.445" end="00:05:19.513">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then at the end of his lesson<br/>he opened up the ice cream cartoon</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.513" end="00:05:22.869">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and there was this real human brain <br/>in formaldehyde.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:22.869" end="00:05:26.071">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everybody freaked out.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:26.071" end="00:05:30.454">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he took us all out for ice cream.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.454" end="00:05:33.719">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In addition to being a surgeon,<br/>my father also wrote best selling books,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:33.719" end="00:05:37.205">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that drew links between disparate fields.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:37.205" end="00:05:39.551">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He searched for patterns <br/>throughout history to give insight</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:39.551" end="00:05:42.301">into why we do what we do.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:42.301" end="00:05:45.706">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In this first book he drew parallels <br/>between breakthroughs in art,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:45.706" end="00:05:48.384">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and breakthroughs in science.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:48.384" end="00:05:52.691">- And you know the artist expresses <br/>the nature of reality</p>
      <p begin="00:05:52.691" end="00:05:54.733">using image and metaphor.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54.733" end="00:05:58.354">And the physicist, he's investigating <br/>the nature of reality</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.354" end="00:06:01.193">and expresses it <br/>using numbers and equations.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01.193" end="00:06:04.083">But it's the same thing<br/>they're just different languages.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:04.083" end="00:06:07.854">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Like how cubism challenged <br/>viewers' notions of space and time,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:07.854" end="00:06:12.231">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">right before Einstein published<br/>his theories about space and time.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:14.133" end="00:06:18.608">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Or how the artist Zoroaster did painting<br/>using tiny dots right around the same time</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:18.608" end="00:06:22.619">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that scientists theorized molecules.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:22.619" end="00:06:27.131">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He found examples like these <br/>throughout history.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:27.131" end="00:06:35.575">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">His books influenced a lot of people.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:35.575" end="00:06:37.457">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Sometimes he was criticized for not being</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:37.457" end="00:06:39.825">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">an expert on the fields he wrote about.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:39.825" end="00:06:41.705">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But I think it was <br/>his outsider perspective</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:41.705" end="00:06:47.396">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that allowed him to see <br/>these bigger connections.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:47.396" end="00:06:50.915">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father could talk about any subject.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:50.915" end="00:06:55.053">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We like to call him "Leonipedia".</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:55.053" end="00:06:58.592">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He and I had been talking about making<br/>a film together for years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:06:58.592" end="00:07:01.230">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So when I started researching<br/>all these connections</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:01.230" end="00:07:04.256">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and how we could use them <br/>to help solve our problems,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:04.256" end="00:07:08.138">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it was natural to ask him <br/>to be one of the co-writers,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:08.138" end="00:07:13.430">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">especially since he and my mom<br/>pretty much co-wrote my brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:13.430" end="00:07:18.179">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I definitely needed help --<br/>just look at my first notes.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:18.179" end="00:07:26.935">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I spent weeks staring at this picture <br/>wondering where to even begin.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:26.935" end="00:07:29.504">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything is so intertwined</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:29.504" end="00:07:33.230">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I thought maybe<br/>that's part of the problem --</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:33.230" end="00:07:38.828">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that we try to deal with all <br/>of these issues in isolation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:38.828" end="00:07:41.622">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Why did we start doing that?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:41.622" end="00:07:45.019">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So I turned to my father <br/>for some perspective.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:45.019" end="00:07:48.699">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said, go to the past <br/>and look for patterns.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:48.699" end="00:07:53.344">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Pretend you're an alien looking<br/>at this unusual species called humans.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:53.344" end="00:07:56.347">&#9834; [humming] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:56.347" end="00:07:57.205">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So I did.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:07:57.205" end="00:07:58.229">[whirring of cameras]</p>
      <p begin="00:07:58.229" end="00:08:00.606">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I hired a narrator to help give that<br/>a mission vibe.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.606" end="00:08:03.251">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I went waaaay back.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:03.251" end="00:08:05.752">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Narrator] [clearing throat] </span></p>
      <p begin="00:08:05.752" end="00:08:09.679">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Once upon a time a single point exploded.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.679" end="00:08:11.196">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:11.196" end="00:08:13.541">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into the universe. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:13.541" end="00:08:16.361">[swishing sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:17.573" end="00:08:22.256">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Which caused the chain reaction <br/>that led to life.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:22.256" end="00:08:24.007">[thunder roaring]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.007" end="00:08:27.610">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For a time dinosaurs lived large.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:27.610" end="00:08:28.982">[dinosaur wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:28.982" end="00:08:29.766">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then not so much.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:29.766" end="00:08:31.936">[splash]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:31.936" end="00:08:35.492">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">One theory of why they died out, <br/>is that they couldn't adapt</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:35.492" end="00:08:41.713">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to the new flowering plants<br/>that depended on bees for pollination.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:41.713" end="00:08:45.947">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Bad news for the dinosaurs,<br/>good news for the bees.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:45.947" end="00:08:48.395">[bees buzzing]</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.395" end="00:08:53.471">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then a new group of <br/>very adaptable mammals emerged.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:53.471" end="00:08:59.557">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They were social, lovable creatures <br/>who love to connect with each other.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:59.557" end="00:09:02.551">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">At first there were very few of them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:02.551" end="00:09:06.924">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But they had a couple of things <br/>going for them, their opposable thumbs</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:06.924" end="00:09:09.762">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which were really good at grasping stuff,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:09.762" end="00:09:12.710">[thud, thud, thud]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:12.710" end="00:09:14.067">[beep, beep, beep]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:14.067" end="00:09:20.692">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and their unusually large brains<br/>which were exceptional at grasping ideas.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:20.692" end="00:09:22.918">[toink]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:22.918" end="00:09:26.286">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The human brain grew rapidly <br/>in early evolution</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:26.286" end="00:09:30.023">not so that they could use tools<br/>or expand their thinking,</p>
      <p begin="00:09:30.023" end="00:09:33.244">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but because of their need to connect.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:33.244" end="00:09:36.330">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Because human babies <br/>are not fully developed,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:36.330" end="00:09:39.929">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">they rely on their parents <br/>longer than other species.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:39.929" end="00:09:46.811">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So human brains evolved<br/>to seek out human contact to survive.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:46.811" end="00:09:49.342">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">These brains are what <br/>distinguished humans</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:49.342" end="00:09:53.171">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">from the other two million <br/>species on earth.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:53.171" end="00:09:55.358">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But for eons they couldn't communicate</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55.358" end="00:09:58.223">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">much of what they knew <br/>about the world with others,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:58.223" end="00:10:00.078">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because they had no written language.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:00.078" end="00:10:01.528">[gasping]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01.528" end="00:10:02.803">[reed stick squeaking]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:02.803" end="00:10:06.639">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Then they finally invented <br/>a radical new technology</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:06.639" end="00:10:08.467">[creaking sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:08.467" end="00:10:10.137">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that would change their lives forever.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:10.137" end="00:10:19.392">[pounding sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:19.392" end="00:10:23.959">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The alphabet made it easier <br/>to keep a narrative record</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:23.959" end="00:10:25.739">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to inform future generations</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:25.739" end="00:10:31.466">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about what had happened <br/>and what had been learned.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:31.466" end="00:10:33.357">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">By accumulating knowledge, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:33.357" end="00:10:43.266">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">humans were able to progress <br/>and multiply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:43.266" end="00:10:48.792">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But literacy also led <br/>to something unexpected.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:48.792" end="00:10:51.034">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">In the <br/>"Alphabet Versus the Goddess" </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:51.034" end="00:10:53.457">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Leonard Shlain points to <br/>how literacy changed</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:53.457" end="00:10:56.778">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the way humans think.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:10:56.778" end="00:11:01.016">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When the alphabet was introduced<br/>into society, it over stimulated</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:01.016" end="00:11:04.410">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the analytic left hemisphere <br/>of the brain. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:04.410" end="00:11:07.094">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He builds on the theory <br/>that the left hemisphere</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:07.094" end="00:11:13.019">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which is used in reading and writing <br/>is associated with masculine traits,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:13.019" end="00:11:16.440">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that the right hemisphere used to see <br/>images and patterns...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:16.440" end="00:11:19.716">[humming]</p>
      <p begin="00:11:19.716" end="00:11:22.358">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is more feminine.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:22.358" end="00:11:27.052">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So Shlain suggests that the advent <br/>of literacy shifted the balance of power</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:27.052" end="00:11:30.923">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">between men and women.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:30.923" end="00:11:35.051">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Well in most ancient societies<br/>men worship the goddesses.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:35.051" end="00:11:38.136">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Whenever literacy was introduced <br/>into a society,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:38.136" end="00:11:43.520">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a new patriarchal outlook emerged.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:43.520" end="00:11:46.394">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He traced this pattern throughout history,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:46.394" end="00:11:49.114">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">finding links between <br/>the onset of literacy</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:49.114" end="00:11:56.085">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and the oppression of women <br/>around the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:56.085" end="00:11:58.511">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Maybe there's a way to build <br/>on my father's ideas</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:11:58.511" end="00:12:00.922">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">about literacy and patriarchy.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:00.922" end="00:12:02.800">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">If he's saying that <br/>the invention of writing </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:02.800" end="00:12:06.274">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">shifted us to a more analytical,<br/>left brain mode of thinking,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:06.274" end="00:12:11.728">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">maybe the shift also led to our tendency <br/>to think of world problems in isolation.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:11.728" end="00:12:14.629">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I can't wait to call my father <br/>to see what he thought about this idea.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:14.629" end="00:12:25.952">[phone ringing]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:25.952" end="00:12:30.611">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But no one picked up.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:12:30.611" end="00:12:33.050">[sirene wailing]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:38.396" end="00:12:40.149">[beeping]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:43.212" end="00:12:44.895">[beeping]</p>
      <p begin="00:12:53.065" end="00:13:05.048">[waves rumbling]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:05.048" end="00:13:10.097">[implosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:16.511" end="00:13:31.184">[whirring of camera]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:31.184" end="00:13:33.383">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:37.075" end="00:13:46.151">[waves rumbling]</p>
      <p begin="00:13:46.151" end="00:13:49.216">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I felt like a child again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:51.960" end="00:13:53.517">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I remember when I was four years old,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:53.517" end="00:13:57.287">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">we were skiing and we're on <br/>one of those really long chairlift rides.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:13:58.892" end="00:14:02.199">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I was just beginning <br/>to get on the ride and I slipped off</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:02.199" end="00:14:05.152">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and my father grabbed <br/>the hood of my coat</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:05.152" end="00:14:07.468">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I was dangling from the chairlift<br/>and he was holding me</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:07.468" end="00:14:10.143">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">with everything he could.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:10.143" end="00:14:12.181">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We were up 40 feet <br/>and there was snow beneath us </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:12.181" end="00:14:15.619">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but we could see rocky cliffs just ahead.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:15.619" end="00:14:18.664">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he looked at me and said, <br/>"I can't hold on to you the whole way."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:18.664" end="00:14:21.088">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"It's safer to let you go <br/>here over the snow."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:21.873" end="00:14:25.843">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I kept saying, <br/>"Daddy, Daddy, don't let me go!"</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:25.843" end="00:14:30.455">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And he looked into my eyes <br/>and he said, "You're gonna be okay."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:30.455" end="00:14:32.028">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he dropped me.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:32.182" end="00:14:34.009">[thud]</p>
      <p begin="00:14:38.119" end="00:14:39.993">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He had to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:46.523" end="00:14:50.405">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And here I was suddenly <br/>feeling the same way,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:50.405" end="00:14:54.462">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">like, "Daddy don't let me go."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:14:54.462" end="00:14:58.726">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I couldn't imagine my world without him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:02.748" end="00:15:04.599">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Those first few days <br/>while he was in the hospital</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:04.599" end="00:15:10.149">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">recovering from brain surgery,<br/>everybody had advice.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:10.149" end="00:15:13.565">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I spoke to this good friend of mine <br/>who had lost his father,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:13.565" end="00:15:18.579">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">he said the most important thing <br/>he could tell me was to film my Dad.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:18.579" end="00:15:21.179">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was his biggest regret<br/>that he hadn't recorded his father</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:21.179" end="00:15:25.150">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">before it was too late.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:25.150" end="00:15:29.164">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I knew I had to start as soon as possible.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:30.318" end="00:15:32.160">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But even though I'd made a lot of films,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:32.160" end="00:15:36.784">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was at a lost on how to capture<br/>my father's essence on film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:36.784" end="00:15:42.461">[waves crashing]</p>
      <p begin="00:15:42.461" end="00:15:44.382">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My father always said <br/>we're the only species</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:44.382" end="00:15:46.352">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that knows we're gonna die,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:46.352" end="00:15:50.569">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that so much of what we do<br/>is driven by that knowledge.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:53.763" end="00:15:55.405">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mother would say <br/>emotional connection</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:15:55.405" end="00:15:59.061">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is what drives everything we do.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:00.308" end="00:16:02.223">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I thought I understood what they meant.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:04.541" end="00:16:05.714">[thunder roaring]</p>
      <p begin="00:16:05.714" end="00:16:09.299">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Death is really abstract until someone<br/>you love is dying right in front of you.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:19.848" end="00:16:21.730">[rattling sound]</p>
      <p begin="00:16:21.730" end="00:16:25.252">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then a few days after my father<br/>was given around nine months to live,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:25.252" end="00:16:27.350">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">my husband Ken and I <br/>found that I was pregnant.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:29.366" end="00:16:33.616">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But we had been <br/>through five miscarriages.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:41.819" end="00:16:43.727">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We'd had an easy time having<br/>our first child.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:43.727" end="00:16:48.558">- [Girl] &#9834; Twinkle twinkle little star<br/>How I wonder what you are. &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:16:50.628" end="00:16:54.806">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But having a second child turned out <br/>to be a lot more difficult.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:16:56.206" end="00:17:00.084">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything felt out of my control,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:02.132" end="00:17:05.649">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">except when I was working on the film.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:05.649" end="00:17:14.665">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:17:14.665" end="00:17:18.342">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything we've been thinking about <br/>suddenly became much more urgent.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:18.396" end="00:17:20.284">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:20.392" end="00:17:22.409">[water gushing]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:22.505" end="00:17:25.254">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What kind of world are we handling<br/>to the next generation?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:25.296" end="00:17:26.375">[explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:26.375" end="00:17:27.761">[people shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:29.322" end="00:17:32.921">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We as humans have accumulated<br/>so much knowledge.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:32.921" end="00:17:35.963">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Why do we have such a hard time<br/>seeing the bigger picture?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:35.963" end="00:17:38.051">[clapping sounds]</p>
      <p begin="00:17:38.051" end="00:17:47.883">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:17:47.883" end="00:17:51.519">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As humans in western civilization <br/>progressed,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:17:51.519" end="00:17:58.007">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">men dominated, and so did <br/>left hemisphere thinking.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:17:58.007" end="00:18:01.770">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Whenever a problem arose,<br/>their strategy was to break it down</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:01.770" end="00:18:07.583">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">into simple parts to solve it.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:07.583" end="00:18:14.366">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They divided and sub-divided, <br/>isolated and analyzed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:14.366" end="00:18:17.186">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They formulated theories <br/>about their discoveries</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:17.186" end="00:18:21.144">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and developed a method <br/>to test those theories.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:21.144" end="00:18:26.740"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They called it</span> science<br/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">after the Greek word meaning</span> to cut.</p>
      <p begin="00:18:26.740" end="00:18:28.404">[cheering and applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:18:28.404" end="00:18:32.473">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This strategy worked so well <br/>that they began slicing and dicing</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:32.473" end="00:18:35.856">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">everything they discovered.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:35.856" end="00:18:38.992">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Classifying and breaking down <br/>everything around them,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:38.992" end="00:18:42.869">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">became a whole way of seeing the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:42.869" end="00:18:48.956">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">For example, they divided beasts <br/>into hundreds of sub-categories.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:48.956" end="00:18:52.277">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A vision of division.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:18:52.277" end="00:18:57.137"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">They even classified their own species,<br/>which they named</span> homo-sapiens,</p>
      <p begin="00:18:57.137" end="00:19:02.635">meaning wise being <br/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">since they were such wise guys.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:19:02.635" end="00:19:05.700">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Their cleverness helped them <br/>to believe that they were different </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:05.700" end="00:19:07.834">from other species.</p>
      <p begin="00:19:07.834" end="00:19:14.845">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So much so that they began thinking of<br/>themselves as independent from nature.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:14.845" end="00:19:17.968">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Entirely.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:17.968" end="00:19:20.272">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Very left brain.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:20.272" end="00:19:28.066">[clicking sounds]</p>
      <p begin="00:19:28.066" end="00:19:32.717">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- My father's tumor was on the left side <br/>of his brain, in the speech center.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:32.717" end="00:19:36.674">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When he came out of surgery<br/>he couldn't speak at all.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:36.674" end="00:19:41.386">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The doctors didn't know if his speech <br/>would ever come back.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:41.386" end="00:19:43.546">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was worried, I would never <br/>hear his voice again,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:45.894" end="00:19:51.081">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that I had already <br/>lost my chance to film him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:19:51.081" end="00:19:58.268">[phone ringing]</p>
      <p begin="00:19:58.268" end="00:20:00.186">[answering machine] <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Hi, this is <br/>Leonard Shlain,</span></p>
      <p begin="00:20:00.186" end="00:20:04.629">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">please leave your name and your <br/>telephone number very slowly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:04.629" end="00:20:06.925">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Thank you so much, bye.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:06.925" end="00:20:09.354">[dial tone]</p>
      <p begin="00:20:09.354" end="00:20:11.307">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- I was so used to calling him <br/>every morning</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:11.307" end="00:20:13.754">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">to talk about everything <br/>that was going on</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:20:13.754" end="00:20:16.525">and it was really hard not to.</p>
      <p begin="00:20:18.033" end="00:20:21.247">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There was so much going through my head.</span>
      </p>
