      <p begin="00:38:33.504" end="00:38:35.811">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that one assassination in Europe,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:35.811" end="00:38:42.034">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">launched a global war that extended <br/>to every continent on earth,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:42.034" end="00:38:45.251">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and that one death led to <br/>fifteen million more.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:45.251" end="00:38:47.290">[gunshots and explosion]</p>
      <p begin="00:38:47.290" end="00:38:50.331">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The war was so devastating <br/>that when it finally ended</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:50.331" end="00:38:53.825">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">it was declared, the war to end all wars.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:38:53.825" end="00:38:57.928">[crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:38:57.928" end="00:39:02.168">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">That eternal peace lasted fifteen years,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:04.835" end="00:39:09.219">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and sixteen million more <br/>human beings died.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:11.360" end="00:39:14.535">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">World War II was the deadliest conflict <br/>in human history.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:14.535" end="00:39:20.439">[bomb exploding]</p>
      <p begin="00:39:20.439" end="00:39:22.699">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">The more connected humans became,</span>
        <br/>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:22.699" end="00:39:27.366">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">the greater the consequences<br/>of their actions.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:27.366" end="00:39:31.659">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What would Madam Curie <br/>have thought?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:31.659" end="00:39:33.505">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">in any interdependent system,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:33.505" end="00:39:38.272">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">every action leads to a chain reaction.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:38.272" end="00:39:39.338">[explosions]</p>
      <p begin="00:39:39.338" end="00:39:42.790">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like in 1958, China's leader <br/>Chairman Mao</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:42.790" end="00:39:45.878">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">initiated the great leap forward.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:45.878" end="00:39:48.596">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">A campaign for progress.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:48.596" end="00:39:52.409">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He wanted to eradicate the sparrows.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:52.409" end="00:39:58.479">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Sparrows he argued, disrupted agriculture,<br/>because they ate grain seeds.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:39:58.479" end="00:40:03.412">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So they tore down the sparrow's nests, <br/>broke the eggs and killed the nestlings.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:05.304" end="00:40:07.842">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">At first then harvest improved,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:07.842" end="00:40:11.793">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">but a few years later, something<br/>unpredictable happened.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:11.793" end="00:40:15.644">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Suddenly, locusts populations exploded</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:15.644" end="00:40:19.727">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">because the sparrows <br/>weren't there to eat them.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:19.727" end="00:40:25.416">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This led to a chain reaction <br/>that destroyed the country's food supply.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:25.416" end="00:40:32.043">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Thirty-six millions humans <br/>died of starvation in three years.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:34.043" end="00:40:40.797">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But sometimes even negative events <br/>can lead to unexpected positive outcomes.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:40.797" end="00:40:44.805">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Announcer] One of the years that <br/>completely reshaped the world we know.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:44.805" end="00:40:47.994">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Man took a giant stride<br/>into the age of the atom</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:47.994" end="00:40:51.478">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and science had the moon in its grasp.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:51.528" end="00:40:54.076"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Take the</span> Cold War --</p>
      <p begin="00:40:55.115" end="00:40:58.085">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a competition between the United States <br/>and the Soviet Union</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:40:59.208" end="00:41:03.921">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which led to two of many <br/>monumental developments.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:03.921" end="00:41:08.238">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Development #. 1 -- the U.S.' drive <br/>to go to the moon,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:08.238" end="00:41:13.217">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which resulted in the first photo <br/>of the earth from outer space.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:15.137" end="00:41:17.251">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Tiffany] And development # 2 - <br/>the Internet</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:17.251" end="00:41:19.244">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">which started from the <br/>U.S. Defense Department</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:19.244" end="00:41:26.199">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">creating a decentralized system of defense <br/>by linking together their computers.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:26.199" end="00:41:30.346">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Every step of progress <br/>has so many ripple effects.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:30.346" end="00:41:35.485">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But no matter how much the world changes <br/>some things never change.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:35.485" end="00:41:40.391">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Like the only thing worse than your <br/>parent getting sick is your child getting sick.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:40.391" end="00:41:41.873">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It was Halloween <br/>and our daughter, Odessa</span>
        <br/>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:41.873" end="00:41:46.104">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">got a severe pain <br/>in the right side of her stomach.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:46.104" end="00:41:48.087">
