      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:56.755" end="00:41:58.347">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But at the hospital, <br/>the doctors wouldn't operate</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:41:58.347" end="00:42:00.696">
