      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:00.696" end="00:42:04.240">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">So we called my father again<br/>and he adamantly disagreed.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:04.240" end="00:42:07.874">
