      <p begin="00:42:07.874" end="00:42:12.075">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">He said don't let the doctors <br/>do this again.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:12.075" end="00:42:16.541">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And then he went to go to sleep<br/>because he was so weak.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:16.541" end="00:42:18.938">
