      <p begin="00:42:41.058" end="00:42:44.756">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">all the way through a major crisis.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:44.756" end="00:42:46.438">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I realized that Ken and I <br/>were gonna have to make</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:46.438" end="00:42:50.318">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">a lot more of this big life decisions <br/>without him.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:51.965" end="00:42:56.239">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everyone experiences that moment when <br/>they become the person who others turn to.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:42:58.547" end="00:43:01.143">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">It's like a big hand-off.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:01.611" end="00:43:06.768">$$ - And you are the person that they're <br/>going to go to.</p>
      <p begin="00:43:09.167" end="00:43:11.043">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Was I ready?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:12.499" end="00:43:18.815">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There comes a time when we all<br/>have to step into the next phase.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:18.815" end="00:43:22.156">
