      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:22.156" end="00:43:25.997">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">family community and the world.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:25.997" end="00:43:28.853">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">As we're becoming more connected, <br/>that impact is only becoming</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:28.853" end="00:43:31.942">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">stronger and faster.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:31.942" end="00:43:36.865">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">But with connections <br/>comes responsibility.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:36.865" end="00:43:39.318">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Are we as a specie ready <br/>to take that on?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:45.841" end="00:43:49.876">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] This left brain way of <br/>thinking became so successful</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:49.876" end="00:43:52.952">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">that humans felt they could create <br/>anything they wanted,</span>
