      </p>
      <p begin="00:43:58.339" end="00:44:03.262">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This insatiable desire to consume <br/>accelerated after World War II</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:44:03.262" end="00:44:07.174">
