      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:12.052" end="00:45:20.307">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Today the average American consumes <br/>195 lbs of stuff every single day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:45:21.321" end="00:45:27.215">
