      </p>
      <p begin="00:47:57.830" end="00:47:59.370">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">is cancer.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:02.109" end="00:48:08.273">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Somewhere along the way, did we lose <br/>our sense of what's important?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:48:18.864" end="00:48:20.876">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Narrator] There's an old story <br/>about a tourist who sees</span>
